&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;https://www.washingtonpost.com/graphics/2018/national/mass-shootings-in-america/?noredirect=on&amp;amp;utm_term=.ddd148a1fe5b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

